content.rendered:
Directed by Santhosh Ananddram.

Written by Santhosh Ananddram.

Cast Puneeth Rajkumar(Siddarth). Priya Anand(Nandini). R. Sarathkumar(Ashok (as Sarath Kumar)). Vijayalakshmi Singh(Sujatha). Anant Nag(Vishwa Joshi). Prakash Raj(Jagannath). Achyuth Kumar(Krishna).H.G. Dattatreya. Ashok(Murthy). Avinash(Jagadeesh). Rangayana Raghu(Venky). Chikkanna(Chikka). Honnavalli Krishna(Muniyappa). Chitra Shenoy(Gayathri). Sadhu Kokila(Anthony Gonsalves). K.S. Sridhar((as K.P. Sridhar)). Anil(Suri) . Ravi Bhat(Family). Ansh Pandit(Shreyas)

Language Kannada.

Producers Vijay Kiragandur. K.V. Rama Rao.

Production Hombale Films.
